  "title": "WSH COORDINATOR",
  "description": "<p>1.Identify their responsibilities under the WSH Act.</p>\n<p>2.Understand WSH policies, procedures and programmes.</p>\n<p>3.Educate workers on WSH policies, procedures and programmes.</p>\n<p>4.Implement and monitor participation and consultation channels for management of WSH.</p>\n<p>5.Implement and monitor the organization’s risk management procedures.</p>\n<p>6.Establish and maintain the framework for the WSH system.</p>\n<p>7.Establish and maintain participation and communication channels for the management of WSH.</p>\n<p>8.Establish and maintain the organization’s risk management procedures.</p>\n<p>9.Evaluate the organization’s WSH system, policies, procedures and programmes.</p>",
